	<h1 class="title">除了谷歌，这些互联网公司的办公室设计也十分酷炫</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1329/small/1329.jpg?1418779602" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡莹</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-11-03 08:12:05 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/3227/medium/3227.jpg?1436637329" alt="" />			
	</div>
